303
00:21:58,960 --> 00:22:01,800
<i>For the times,
they are a-changin’</i>

304
00:22:01,840 --> 00:22:04,560
<i>There’s no question.
The First Cavalry Division...</i>

305
00:22:04,600 --> 00:22:06,520
<i>is the latest concept in mobile warfare.</i>

306
00:22:06,560 --> 00:22:08,280
<i>Just one of those divisions is worth...</i>

307
00:22:08,320 --> 00:22:11,000
<i>two and a half Russian
