00:36:37,480 --> 00:36:40,280
It’s so hot out here,
I want to kill some motherfucking gooks.

471
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:42,520
Dog, you’re sounding
like a bitch, man.

472
00:36:42,560 --> 00:36:44,360
Ain’t nothing but a thing.

473
00:36:48,120 --> 00:36:51,280
It’s so hot out in this motherfucker,
this must be hell.

474
00:36:53,760 --> 00:36:55,200
Or purgatory.

475
00:36:57,760 --> 00:37:00,000
