02:10:17,040 --> 02:10:20,800
It’s been a long way to get here.
Tell them what it is, Ron.

1639
02:10:21,600 --> 02:10:23,160
Come on, Ronnie.

1640
02:10:23,920 --> 02:10:25,360
Go get them, man.
For Eddie, man.

1641
02:10:25,400 --> 02:10:27,160
Ronnie for President!

1642
02:10:27,720 --> 02:10:30,080
The whole world’s watching.
I love you.

1643
02:10:30,160 --> 02:10:31,800
All right, Frankie.

1644
02:10:31,840 --> 02:10:33,320
I feel good.

1645
02:10:33,360 --> 02:10:35,120
Ronnie for President.

1646
02:10:36,240 --> 02:10:37,800
Congratulations.

1647
02:10:39,200 --> 02:10:40,720
I love what you’re doing.

1648
02:10:40,760 --> 02:10:44,320
Clear a path for me, please.
Stand back. Thank you.

1649
02:10:46,920 --> 02:10:48,360
<i>I had a dream, Ronnie.</i>

1650
02:10:48,440 --> 02:10:50,960
<i>You were speaking to a large crowd.</i>

1651
02:10:51,600 --> 02:10:53,920
<i>And you were saying great things.</i>

1652
02:11:02,320 --> 02:11:06,240
<i>Our next speaker is one
of our Vietnam veterans...</i>

1653
02:11:06,760 --> 02:11:09,800
<i>who has something very special
to say tonight.</i>

1654
02:11:11,240 --> 02:11:12,400
<i>Please...</i>

1655
02:11:13,840 --> 02:11:15,440
<i>please be quiet.</i>

1656
02:11:15,520 --> 02:11:16,640
Coming up top.

1657
02:11:16,720 --> 02:11:19,200
What will you say tonight, Mr. Kovic?

1658
02:11:19,800 --> 02:11:23,160
- I’m just going to tell the truth.
- Any plans for the future?

1659
02:11:23,760 --> 02:11:25,040
I guess we’ll see.

1660
02:11:25,080 --> 02:11:27,560
Mr. Kovic, could you please
sign your book?

1661
02:11:27,600 --> 02:11:31,280
<i>A young man who comes
from Massapequa, Long Island.</i>

1662
02:11:32,560 --> 02:11:34,240
Coming through.

1663
02:11:34,320 --> 02:11:37,040
All right, sweetheart.
Straight on through.

1664
02:11:37,120 --> 02:11:39,760
How does it feel
to address the entire country?

1665
02:11:41,520 --> 02:11:43,840
Overwhelming, an honor....

1666
02:11:44,040 --> 02:11:46,600
It’s been a long way for us, the vets.

1667
02:11:47,240 --> 02:11:51,720
Just lately, I’ve felt like I’m home.

1668
02:11:53,080 --> 02:11:55,840
Like, maybe we’re home.

1669
02:11:57,560 --> 02:11:59,600
Welcome home, Ronnie.

1670
02:11:59,640 --> 02:12:01,240
Go get them, Ron!
